          <h1 id="bpd_title" class="bpd-post-title">Implementing QR Code Payments in Your Business: A Complete Guide</h1>
          <div id="bpd_metadata" class="bpd-post-meta">
            <div class="author-avatar" aria-hidden="true">SP</div>
            <span class="author-name">Sarah Parker</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">·</span>
